data.description: Kempsville area modern farmhouse with large front sitting porch overlooking a lake.  Cul de sac location with privacy fenced back yard.  Four levels include a basement and walk-up attic. Storage galore.  Light filled home. Attached oversized 2 car garage.  New LVP flooring and fresh paint throughout.  Updated LED lighting. Covered rear sitting porch.  Inground pool.  Main level with full bath and bedroom / office. Wood burning fireplace.  Very large primary bedroom with walk-in closet and ensuite.  Primary bath with marble countertop, enclosed camode, walk-in shower and tub.  Ideal commuter location to I 64 / 264, shopping, restaurants and recreation. Minutes to Town Center.
